Design/set-up specific written policy on the submission of documents and its integral parts upon approval of a perfected contract, and to furnish the Office of the Auditor a copy of  the contract/s and its supporting documents within five (5) working days for review in accordance with COA Circular No. 87-278 dated November 12, 1987; and

Submit colored photographs taken (before, on-going and after) duly labelled, and when possible, the date and time it was taken would appear on the bottom or elsewhere in the picture, for all projects completed/implemented by the City.

Use the secondary data coming from the City’s monitoring system and/or various operating units of the different departments as an initial input data in addressing GAD related issues.  Carefully analyze the information to support identified gender issues in the preparation and formulation of GAD plans and programs for the ensuing year while waiting for the completion of the GAD database and sex disaggregated data; and

